title: Emily Hampshire
itunes:title: Emily Hampshire
description:
Actress Emily Hampshire (SCHITT'S CREEK, 12 MONKEYS, MOTHER!) comes on the pod this week and discovers she and Whitney are the same person.  Then they get into butthole bleaching and Michael Jackson.  Emily's narrative podcast THE BEAUTIFUL LIAR is out now. 

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
